      <li>Agreement: There is a round after which all honest parties return the same output if queried by the environment.</li>

      <li>Validity: The output returned by an honest party <span class="math">P</span> equals the input of some party <span class="math">P^{\\prime}</span> that is honest at the round <span class="math">P</span>s output is produced.</li>

    </ol>

